    <div class="table-responsive mb-4">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Key Differentiators:</h2>
        <ul class="list-group-horizontal">
            <li><b>Standards Compliance: </b>PrivacyConfirmed offers a more comprehensive set of compliance certifications tailored to global and India-specific regulations like ISO, SOC, and GDPR</li>
            <li><b>Single Sign-On (SSO): </b>Unlike some competitors, PrivacyConfirmed offers out-of-the-box support for multiple SSO integrations (Google, Facebook, LinkedIn, custom solutions)</li>
            <li><b>Social Login: </b>PrivacyConfirmed supports a wide range of social login options, enabling flexible user authentication across your apps</li>
            <li><b>Enterprise Features: </b>PrivacyConfirmed offers Role-Based Access Control (RBAC), Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA), detailed audit logs, and policy enforcement, providing a complete enterprise security suite</li>
            <li><b>India-Specific Data Residency: </b>PrivacyConfirmed is India-first, offering data residency options within India to comply with local regulations, and local support tailored for Indian businesses</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="table-responsive mb-5">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Legal & Compliance</h2>
        <strong class="d-block mb-3">ISO/SOC Readiness</strong>
        <p>PrivacyConfirmed IAM is ISO and SOC compliant, ensuring that your organization meets the highest global standards for security, confidentiality, and privacy. This includes:</p>
        <ul class="list-group-horizontal">
            <li>ISO 27001: Information Security Management System (ISMS) to safeguard your data.</li>
            <li>SOC 2: Ensures that PrivacyConfirmed follows rigorous standards for security, availability, confidentiality, processing integrity, and privacy.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-xxl-5">These certifications provide a clear framework for managing sensitive information, giving your organization the confidence it needs to maintain compliance with industry regulations.</p>
    </div>
